{
  "stem": "22469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was divide with-- with wires, and police-- Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] The ghetto A, this was working people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And ghetto B, what they don't-- didn't work this time-- old people, children, and not-working people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this 13 of March, '43, after they surrounded, they took from ghetto A, every people to the barracks on the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they left-- they left what is-- they stay in the ghetto B.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came-- this was Saturday-- when we came to the cemetery, they give us order to dig a big huge-- I-- we didn't know-- huge grave.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we get a little suspicion why we're digging.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was taking until morning, 4 o'clock in the morning. 9 o'clock, was a Sunday, next day, they start to bring dead people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They shot every single one was in ghetto B-- they was shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they brought them to this big grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We buried them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the end of ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This cemetery, this is area, this was called Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was just SS and barracks, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we haven't got very, very little to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in, I think, after five days, the SS surrounded every barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, everything what we got-- money, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] gold-- everything which was valuable, to get up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In our barracks, the-- one SS told us, if we don't give everything, we're going to be like this one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he shot one of us, just to example of what are you going to be if we don't give them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they took everything from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After-- after one or two weeks, I personally was appointed decorator.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
